    <briefdescription>
<para>ROS2 node that manages a Soar kernel and its agents. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Responsibilities:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Own the sml::Kernel and the spin thread.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Create sml::Agent instances on request and wrap them in <ref refid="classsoar__ros_1_1SoarAgent" kindref="compound">SoarAgent</ref>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Expose ROS2 service interfaces to start/stop the kernel and launch the Soar Java debugger.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>I/O wiring is done on each <ref refid="classsoar__ros_1_1SoarAgent" kindref="compound">SoarAgent</ref> returned from <ref refid="classsoar__ros_1_1SoarRunner_1abc859374ab38dd9cf0245cedb94f1fed" kindref="member">addAgent()</ref>, not here. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
